ActMeat Inspection Act
PrecisRegulations Amending the MEAT INSPECTION REGULATIONS, 1990 by allowing foods containing both meat and fish to be classified as either a fish product or a meat product, depending on the composition of the food, its traditional use and the nature of the processing used.
